{"tid":889410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國貿易戰指揮: 雷泰沙","createTime":"2018-11-04T14:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T15:17:29.000Z","uid":98832,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f529dcbc6f8bad30e2f7637f5e12480e29130c24","tid":889410,"uid":98832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d8/Robert_E._Lighthizer_official_portrait.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd8%2FRobert_E._Lighthizer_official_portrait.jpg&h=b07e8787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n侵侵任命的美國貿易代表，Robert Lighthizer，暫譯雷泰沙，係中美貿易戰的指揮官。佢應該係神經刀內閣唯一成員有完整連貫的政經哲學同埋執行能力。<br />\n<br />\n雷泰沙係Georgetown 讀完law degree，做了幾年律師就幫共和黨的Bob Dole做事。雷根年代，佢三十出頭，就任美國副貿易代表，同時係美日投資委員會主席，其中負責日本鋼鐵入口。(.....相傳中國政府最驚的廣場協議入面對日本部份，佢有份幫手修訂。) 雷泰沙做了幾年就辭職去幫舊老闆Bob Dole選總統。當然大家都知Bob Dole選唔到, 咁雷泰沙就返去Skadden執葉。<br />\n<br />\n廿年後的今日，侵侵搵雷泰沙出山，再續雷根年代對付日本的劇本，不過個奸角就係行緊國家資本主義的中國。<br />\n<br />\n雷泰沙絕對係自由貿易支持者, 但多年國際貿易經驗令佢明白到自由貿易要有一個公平的營商環境。試問一間美國大型上市公司，受多樣先進國家法規限制同埋國內市場競爭，點同一間國家資本主義下的(半)國有企業打? 對手有多種非對稱優勢，下列數點:國有銀行亂批貸款、國內市場無競爭、政府直接補貼。雷泰沙希望自己國家隊落埋場，達致真正有競爭的市場經濟。<br />\n<br />\nSources:<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/08/06/you-live-in-robert-lighthizers-world-now-trump-trade/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fyou-live-in-robert-lighthizers-world-now-trump-trade%2F&d=BceRMzIzTQxwWEDj4COd1Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fcf3f3d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/08/06/you-live-in-robert-lighthizers-world-now-trump-trade/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/people/robert-lighthizer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpeople%2Frobert-lighthizer%2F&d=BceRMzIzTQxwWEDj4COd1Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=017309d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitehouse.gov/people/robert-lighthizer/</a>"},{"pid":"dd7d5e227067dbb564c0741222fdc936d0b22304","tid":889410,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec13e75fefbf451f1f041ef508e16933294e9466","tid":889410,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d1f4da539de5cb80360af96ff9c5f20b51c047","tid":889410,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"最緊要令支那爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}